# ============================================
# NOTES
# ============================================
# 1. All NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables are exposed to the browser
# 2. Other variables are server-side only
# 3. After changing environment variables in Vercel, redeploy your application
# 4. Use different API keys for production vs. development when possible
# 5. Rotate API keys periodically for security
# 6. Monitor API usage to avoid unexpected costs
